    function showMenu()
 	    {
 	        var menu = document.getElementById("rolloutmenu");
 	        var content = document.getElementById("content");
 	        if (menu == null || content == null)
 	            return;
 	        if (menu.style.display == "none") 
 	        {
 	            menu.style.display = "block"; 
 	            content.style.display = "none"; 
 	        }
 	        else
 	        {
 	            menu.style.display = "none"; 
 	            content.style.display = "block";
 	        } 
 	    }
 	    
 	    function hideMenu()
 	    {
 	        var menu = document.getElementById("rolloutmenu");
 	        var content = document.getElementById("content");
 	        if (menu == null || content == null)
 	            return;
 	        menu.style.display = "none"; 
 	        content.style.display = "block";
 	    }
   </script>

      <script type="text/javascript">
       var currentItem = 1;
     var nextItem; 
     var opacity = 0; 
    
    // Set timeout
     var repeatTime = 0;  
    
     function setNextItem()
     {
         // Check for next item 
         var newItem = currentItem + 1; 
         var item1 = document.getElementById("ctl00_ContentPlaceHolder1_photogallery_photo" + newItem);
         if (item1 == null)
             newItem = 1;
             
         changeItem(newItem);
         
         // Set repeat
         if (repeatTime > 0)
         {
             clearTimeout(move);
             move = setTimeout(setNextItem, repeatTime);
         }
     } 
    
     function setPreviousItem()
     {
         // Check for next item 
         var newItem = currentItem - 1; 
         var item1 = document.getElementById("ctl00_ContentPlaceHolder1_photogallery_photo" + newItem);
         if (item1 == null)
             newItem = getLastItem();
             
         changeItem(newItem);
         
         // Set repeat
         if (repeatTime > 0)
         {
             clearTimeout(move);
             move = setTimeout(setPreviousItem, repeatTime);
         }
     }  
    
     function getLastItem()
     {
         var i; 
         for (i = 20; i >= 1; i--)
         {
             var item1 = document.getElementById("ctl00_ContentPlaceHolder1_photogallery_photo" + i);
             if (item1 != null)
                 return i;
         } 
         
         return 1;
     }       
    
     function changeItem(newItem, restartTime) 
     {
         if (currentItem == newItem)
             return;
             
         if (opacity > 0)
             return;
         
         // Set labels
         var label1 = document.getElementById("ctl00_ContentPlaceHolder1_photogallery_label" + currentItem);
         var label2 = document.getElementById("ctl00_ContentPlaceHolder1_photogallery_label" + newItem);
         if (label1 != null)
         {
             label1.setAttribute("class", "label"); 
             label1.setAttribute("className", "label"); 
         }
         if (label2 != null)
         {
             label2.setAttribute("class", "selectedlabel"); 
             label2.setAttribute("className", "selectedlabel"); 
         }
         
         // Set photo
         nextItem = newItem;
         opacity = 1;
         swap();
         if (repeatTime > 0)
         {
             // Set restart time for auto roate
             clearTimeout(move);
             move = setTimeout(setNextItem, restartTime);
         }
     }  
    
     function swap()
     { 
         var item1 = document.getElementById("ctl00_ContentPlaceHolder1_photogallery_photo" + currentItem);
         var item2 = document.getElementById("ctl00_ContentPlaceHolder1_photogallery_photo" + nextItem);
         
         opacity -= 0.1
         item1.xOpacity = opacity;
         setOpacity(item1);
         item2.style.display = "block";
         item2.xOpacity = 1 - opacity;
         setOpacity(item2);
 
         if (opacity <= 0)
         {
             opacity = 0;
             item1.xOpacity = 0;
             item2.xOpacity = 1;
             setOpacity(item2);
             item1.style.display = "none";
             currentItem = nextItem;
             return;
         }
         
         setTimeout(swap, 50);
     }   
    
     function setOpacity(obj)
     {
         if (obj.xOpacity>.99)
         {
             obj.xOpacity = .99;
             return;
         }
         obj.style.opacity = obj.xOpacity;
         obj.style.MozOpacity = obj.xOpacity;
         obj.style.filter = "alpha(opacity=" + (obj.xOpacity*100) + ")";
    }
      </script>
      <script type="text/javascript">

       <div class="centre">
        <div class="text">
         <h1>
          Bed &amp; Breakfast in Dorchester
         </h1>
         <p>
          <span style="font-size:14px">
           <span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif">
            <em>
             "Heaven on Earth" - Larraine &amp; Tony Edwards, Guestbook, May 2018
            </em>
           </span>
          </span>
         </p>
         <p>
          <span style="font-size:14px">
           <span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif">
            <strong>
             We are pleased to announce that we are now supporting the Jurassic Coast Trust as a business partner. Read more
             <a href="http://www.aquilaheights.co.uk/news/27">
              here
             </a>
             .
            </strong>
           </span>
          </span>
         </p>
         <p>
          <span style="font-size:14px">
           <span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif">
            Aquila Heights is a friendly and comfortable guest house offering quality B&amp;B accommodation in Dorchester. Our south-facing Edwardian house has 6 individual light and airy bedrooms offering modern facilities and original period character.
           </span>
          </span>
         </p>
         <p>
          R
          <span style="background-color:transparent; color:rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size:14px">
           anked No 1 on
          </span>
          <a href="https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/Hotel_Review-g186263-d631625-Reviews-Aquila_Heights_Guest_House-Dorchester_Dorset_England.html" style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(7, 130, 193); font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: underline; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px;" target="_blank">
           TripAdvisor
          </a>
          <span style="background-color:transparent; color:rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size:14px">
           for Dorchester and the surrounding area.
          </span>
         </p>
         <ul>
          <li>
           <span style="font-size:14px">
            <span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif">
             Home from home comfort, with large extra-length beds, quality bedding and well stocked bathrooms
            </span>
           </span>
          </li>
          <li>
           <span style="font-size:14px">
            <span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif">
             The indulgent Aquila breakfast - loads and loads of choice, lots of local Dorset ingredients, all freshly prepared and cooked to order
            </span>
           </span>
          </li>
          <li>
           <span style="font-size:14px">
            <span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif">
             Free off-road parking. Free high-speed fibre WiFi. Freeview TV
            </span>
           </span>
          </li>
          <li>
           <span style="font-size:14px">
            <span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif">
             Hospitality trays with choice of teas, coffees, hot chocolate, water and local Dorset biscuits
            </span>
           </span>
          </li>
          <li>
           <span style="font-size:14px">
            <span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif">
             Secure dry overnight cycle storage. Rental bikes delivered direct to the door. Wet clothes drying for cyclists and walkers
            </span>
           </span>
          </li>
          <li>
           <span style="font-size:14px">
            <span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif">
             Free collection and return from railway and coach stations
            </span>
           </span>
          </li>
          <li>
           <span style="font-size:14px">
            <span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif">
             Quiet, easy to find location. Walking distance to the town centre and ideal for touring and exploring West Dorset, Hardy Country and the Jurassic Coast.
            </span>
           </span>
          </li>
          <li>
           <span style="font-size:14px">
            <span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif">
             Panoramic views from the bedrooms include the ramparts of Maiden Castle, Hardy's Monument &amp; the
            </span>
            South Dorset Ridgeway.
           </span>
          </li>
         </ul>
         <p>
          <span style="font-size:14px">
           <span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif">
            Now
            <a href="http://www.aquilaheights.co.uk/book">
             booking
            </a>
            for all of 2018.
           </span>
          </span>
         </p>
         <p>
          <span style="font-size:14px">
           <span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif">
            <em>
             "The welcome, service, room and food were simply the best we have experienced" - Steviebarley, TripAdvisor, October 2016
            </em>
           </span>
          </span>
         </p>

       <script type="text/javascript">
        var move;   
     var count = 0; 
     function moveGallery(distance, viewWidth, totalWidth, stepSize, scrollTime, distanceMoved)
     { 
         if (distance == 0)
             return;
              
         // Validate step size & distance
         if (stepSize >= 0 && stepSize < 1)
             stepSize = 1;
         if (stepSize <= 0 && stepSize > -1)
             stepSize = -1;
              
         // Get panel & holder
         var viewer = document.getElementById("roomcaptions");
         if (distance > 0 && viewer.scrollLeft < totalWidth - viewWidth)
         {   
             if (stepSize > distance - distanceMoved)
             {
                 viewer.scrollLeft += distance - distanceMoved;
                 distanceMoved = distance;
             }  
             else 
             {
                 viewer.scrollLeft += stepSize;
                 distanceMoved += stepSize 
             } 
         }
         if (distance < 0)
         {
             if (Math.abs(stepSize) > Math.abs(distance) - Math.abs(distanceMoved))
             {
                 viewer.scrollLeft += distance - distanceMoved;
                 distanceMoved = distance; 
             }
             else
             {
                 viewer.scrollLeft += stepSize;
                 distanceMoved += stepSize; 
             }
             if (viewer.scrollLeft < 0)
             {
                 viewer.scrollLeft = 0; 
                 distanceMoved = distance;
             }  
         }
                     
         // Enable/disable arrows
         var previous = document.getElementById("ctl00_ContentPlaceHolder1_roomcaptions_imgPrevious");
         var next = document.getElementById("ctl00_ContentPlaceHolder1_roomcaptions_imgNext");
         if (viewer.scrollLeft <= 0)
         {
             previous.disabled = true;
             previous.src = "/images/base/prev_disabled.jpg";  
         }
         else
         {
             previous.disabled = false;
             previous.src = "/images/base/prev.jpg";  
         } 
         if (viewer.scrollLeft >= totalWidth - viewWidth)
         {
             next.disabled = true;
             next.src = "/images/base/next_disabled.jpg";  
         }
         else
         {
             next.disabled = false;
             next.src = "/images/base/next.jpg";  
         } 
         
         ++count;
         if (Math.abs(distanceMoved) < Math.abs(distance))
         {
             var repeatTime = scrollTime * stepSize / distance;
             move = setTimeout("moveGallery(" + distance + "," + viewWidth + "," + totalWidth + "," + stepSize + "," + scrollTime + "," + distanceMoved + ")", repeatTime);
         }
         else
         {
             clearTimeout(move);
             if (viewer.scrollLeft % viewWidth > viewWidth - 10)
                 viewer.scrollLeft += viewWidth - (viewer.scrollLeft % viewWidth);
             count = 0;
         }
     }
       </script>
